    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Code Trainer</strong> is an educational tool for improving your coding skills. Solve problems, complete quizzes, and learn about common computer science topics.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Code</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Practice your problem-solving skills to prepare for interviews or for fun! Write real code in Python, JavaScript, Java, or C#. All code runs locally on your computer so there is no need for an internet connection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294190/extras/b77c25cde68c7681029b1c8d51079406.poster.avif?t=1732010719\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294190/extras/b77c25cde68c7681029b1c8d51079406.mp4?t=1732010719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Quiz</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Been a while since you've brushed up on the basics? Engage in different quizzes to make sure you have well-rounded knowledge of various computer science topics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294190/extras/eb4b4d1f4d3cca9901e4c179fd5243f5.avif?t=1732010719\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294190/extras_big/eb4b4d1f4d3cca9901e4c179fd5243f5.avif?t=1732010719 width=800 height=463 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Review concise courses about Data Structures, Algorithms, Software Development, and more with interactive features to solidify your conceptual understanding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294190/extras/573c10d7547506c195827c8f318b5cc2.avif?t=1732010719\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294190/extras_big/573c10d7547506c195827c8f318b5cc2.avif?t=1732010719 width=800 height=463 /></span></p>",
